flowchart TD
    START([Start]) --> OPEN[Open VideoCapture]
    OPEN --> READ{Read Frame}
    READ -->|EOF| FINALIZE[Finalize ALPR\nfor active tracks]
    FINALIZE --> CSV_FINAL[Append remaining\nrows to CSV]
    CSV_FINAL --> DONE([Done])

    READ -->|Frame| SKIP{Frame skip\ncheck}
    SKIP -->|Skip| READ
    SKIP -->|Process| RESIZE[Resize to 640px]

    RESIZE --> DETECT[YOLOv11 Inference\nclasses: vehicle/person]
    DETECT --> TRACK[ByteTrack\nAssociation]
    TRACK --> FOREACH[For each tracked vehicle]

    FOREACH --> CROP[Crop vehicle bbox]
    CROP --> PLATE_DET{Plate detector\navailable?}
    PLATE_DET -->|Yes| PLATE_INF[YOLO plate inference\non crop]
    PLATE_DET -->|No| HEURISTIC[Lower-half heuristic]
    PLATE_INF --> OCR_RUN[EasyOCR on\nenhanced plate region]
    HEURISTIC --> OCR_RUN
    OCR_RUN --> VALIDATE{Pakistan\nformat valid?}
    VALIDATE -->|Yes| ACCUMULATE[Accumulate reading\nfor track ID]
    VALIDATE -->|No| ACCUMULATE

    ACCUMULATE --> COUNTER[Update sliding\nwindow counter]
    COUNTER --> CSV_ROW[Write sampled\nCSV detection row]

    CSV_ROW --> FUSION[Accident Fusion\nevaluate all pairs]
    FUSION --> SIGNALS{≥ min_signals\nfor ≥ confirm_seconds?}
    SIGNALS -->|No| ANNOTATE
    SIGNALS -->|Yes| SAVE_MEDIA[Save snapshot + clip]
    SAVE_MEDIA --> ALERT[Dispatch WhatsApp\n+ SMTP alerts async]
    ALERT --> CSV_ACC[Write accident rows\nto CSV]
    CSV_ACC --> ANNOTATE[Draw overlays\non frame]

    ANNOTATE --> WRITE[Write to output MP4]
    WRITE --> READ
